dule.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e● Knowledge of Microsoft Office (Word, Power Point, Excel).\u003cbr/\u003e● Experience using Muckrack/LEFTY influencer tracking is a plus, but is not required\u003cbr/\u003e● Experience with executing client events is a plus, but not required.\u003cbr/\u003e● Must be detailed oriented, possess strong organizational and time management skills, solutions oriented.\u003cbr/\u003e● Positive, proactive and hard-working attitude.\u003cbr/\u003e● Ability to assist and lead on multiple client accounts at once.\u003cbr/\u003e● Eager to work in a very fast-paced industry.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://michelemariepr.com/?\" rel=\"noopener\" onclick=\"return phoenixTrackClickEvent(this, event);\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eMMPR\u003c/a\u003e offers competitive salaries and hybrid schedules, Medical, Vision and Dental benefits, 401k, short day Fridays year round, Perk Program, 3 weeks paid vacations, and paid PTO.\u003cbr/\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e\u003cbr/\u003eCompensation\u003c/strong\u003e: Starting salary $55k, dependent on experience.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eTo Apply: Please send your resume to \u003ca href=\"mailto:jobs@michelemariepr.com\"\u003ejobs@michelemariepr.com\u003c/a\u003e, subject line \u003cem\u003eBeauty SAE.\u003c/em\u003e\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://michelemariepr.com/?\" rel=\"noopener\" onclick=\"return phoenixTrackClickEvent(this, event);\" target=\"_blank\"\u003emichelemariepr.com\u003c/a\u003e\u003cbr/\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.instagram.com/michelemariepr/\" rel=\"noopener\" onclick=\"return phoenixTrackClickEvent(this, event);\" target=\"_blank\"\u003e@michelemariepr\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003csection id=\"phx-3\"\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eScroll to Continue\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cdiv id=\"phx-5\"\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ch2 role=\"heading\" aria-level=\"2\"\u003eRecommended Articles\u003c/h2\u003e\